data.description: You are sure to fall in love with this remarkable 4-bedroom, 3-full-bath residence nestled on a quiet cul-de-sac in the neighborhood of Chestnut Hills. Boasting over 3500 square foot of living space, a symphony of sleek lines, clean angles, and loads of natural light, this home embodies the essence of a contemporary style home. The generously sized living room is adorned with gorgeous wood beams that add even more warmth and character to the space. The gorgeous kitchen is spacious and offers modern functionality with a large island, hardwood floors, loads of counter space and a beautiful backsplash. This kitchen offers high-end appliances including a double-oven, clean and abundant cabinetry and a seamless layout to the dining room.  Entertain in style with the sleek bar area/kitchenette on the lower level that serves as a focal point for social gatherings and includes a walk out to the beautiful, fenced back yard. The serene outdoor entertaining area includes both a large deck and patio area, spiral staircase to upper level and most of the landscaping his been professionally done providing a perfect backdrop for entertaining or quiet moments of reflection. Two bedrooms are located on the main level and two bedrooms on lower level. All four bedrooms are ample in size!  This home and property are stunning, so set up your showing today!
